{"tid":2218373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲：世界必須盡力了解武漢肺炎起源","createTime":"2020-09-26T07:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T08:12:01.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"94e8580fd1821a642161be2ed4a7c95c042b8f10","tid":2218373,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"莫里森：世界必須盡力了解新型冠狀病毒起源<br />\n<br />\n澳洲總理莫里森在聯合國大會表示，世界必須盡一切努力了解新型冠狀病毒起源，說病毒為世界造成災難，要了解發生甚麼事，阻止事件再次發生。他說要確定病毒的人畜共通病源，和病毒是如何傳播予人類。澳洲早前因主張對新型冠狀病毒起源展開國際獨立調查，導致中澳關係緊張。北京對澳洲實施貿易限制，暫停當地部份牛肉進口，又對當地葡萄酒進口發起反傾銷調查。<br />\n<br />\n另外，澳洲呼籲所有國家共享疫苗，又說會與太平洋島國共享醫療物資。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2359030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2359030&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTuxSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=18da6ce5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2359030</a>"},{"pid":"20c01231c8500b6d3b67395ad117c98947d6536e","tid":2218373,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:13:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a535f186da8145bd046dcf49f977f6034d001867","tid":2218373,"uid":56819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:14:44.000Z","msg":"係人都知係支共搞出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fffc27563380c3621a8b6fcbce2f13ce1a6591a","tid":2218373,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/a3d50dc7c2d9cb4096c3bd39e2040683/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fa3d50dc7c2d9cb4096c3bd39e2040683%2Ftenor.gif&h=d21ff527&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}